    <comment>- update to 8.1.1:
  * Hotfix for animation on complete
- update to 8.1.0:
  * Replace circuar references in DOM with weak references to
    improve GC times
  * When animating an attribute a second time, the original
    `on_complete` is now called
- update to 8.0.2:
  * Themes are now in alphabetical order in command palette
  * Fixed issues with Directory Tree</comment>
