  <revision rev="8" vrev="1">
    <srcmd5>2bfeb64f14c3962d046446d20670167f</srcmd5>
    <version>8.2.1</version>
    <time>1774888284</time>
    <user>anag_factory</user>
    <comment>- update to 8.2.1:
  * Fixes a crash when a selected widget is removed while
    selecting
  * Fix crash when a widget disapears between selections
- update to 8.2.0:
  * This release enhances text selection, with auto-scrolling,
    and the ability to select across container widgets.
  * Auto-scrolling on select
  * Selecting over containers
  * Added `App.ENABLE_SELECT_AUTO_SCROLL`,
    `App.SELECT_AUTO_SCROLL_LINES`,
    `App.SELECT_AUTO_SCROLL_SPEED` to tweak auto scrolling
    behavior</comment>
    <requestid>1343521</requestid>
  </revision>
